　　民　　國　 110　　年　　1 　　月　　26　　日\r\n                              書  記  官  宋庭華","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CPEM/110%2c%e7%ab%b9%e5%8c%97%e7%b0%a1%2c59%2c20210413%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CPEM,110,竹北簡,59,20210413,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"竹北簡","JNO":"59","JDATE":"20210413","JTITLE":"傷害"}